        "html": "<section class='py-20 bg-white'>\n  <div class='max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6'>\n    <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 text-center'>Book an Appointment</h2>\n    <p class='text-gray-500 mb-10 text-center'>Choose a service, pick a time, and we will confirm within 1 business hour.</p>\n    <form class='bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-6'>\n      <div>\n        <label class='block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2'>Service</label>\n        <select class='w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-400'>\n          <option>Select a service…</option>\n          <option>Consultation (30 min)</option>\n          <option>Full Service (1 hr)</option>\n          <option>Premium Package (2 hrs)</option>\n        </select>\n      </div>\n      <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4'>\n        <div>\n          <label class='block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2'>Preferred Date</label>\n          <input type='date' class='w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-400'>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <label class='block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2'>Preferred Time</label>\n          <select class='w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-400'>\n            <option>Morning (9–12)</option>\n            <option>Afternoon (12–5)</option>\n            <option>Evening (5–8)</option>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4'>\n        <div>\n          <label class='block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2'>First Name</label>\n          <input type='text' placeholder='Jane' class='w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-400'>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <label